  "title": "Xtra Lazy Canadian Chickpeas Skillet",
  "description": "A funky, shattering, lazy-Sunday Canadian dish featuring a can of chickpeas, deglaze, and Mediterranean-friendly flavors, perfect for a relaxing day at home.",
